                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18430612-1820-offence-1 t18430612-cd-88"></join>19th of May</rs>, 2 printed books, value 20<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18430612-name-697" type="victimName">
